Define LibPub newton_raphson(f,df,x0,tol,maxiter)=
Func
:Local x,xnew,iter,error_val,fx,dfx
:x0→x
:0→iter
:tol+1→error_val
:
:While error_val>tol and iter<maxiter
:  expr(f)|x=x→fx
:  expr(df)|x=x→dfx
:
:  If abs(dfx)<1.−14 Then
:    Return "Error: Zero derivative"
:  EndIf
:
:  x-((fx)/(dfx))→xnew
:abs(xnew-x)→error_val
:  xnew→x
:  iter+1→iter
:EndWhile
:
:If iter≥maxiter Then
:  Return "Max iterations Reached"
:Else
:  Return x
:EndIf
:EndFunc